headline: Lilly opens newest Gateway Labs site in San Diego to boost local biotechnology ecosystem
summary: Eli Lilly and Company (NYSE: LLY) today announced the official opening of its newest Lilly Gateway Labs (LGL) site in San Diego, California, expanding its network of shared innovation hubs designed to support early-stage biotechnology companies by providing lab space and opportunities to collaborate with Lilly scientists.
